Pre-Game Insights: Twenty-two-year-old Rhett Lowder will make his fourth start for Cincinnati.
Twenty-four-year old David Festa will make his 11th start for the Twins.
Rhett Lowder has given up one run over 15 1/3 innings in his first three starts.
David Festa has received mixed reviews through his first 10 starts and has lost four in a row.
